<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{title}}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 2rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 1rem 0;
        }
        .user-info {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 1rem 0;
        }
        .api-links {
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }
        .api-links a {
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 0.5rem 1rem 0.5rem 0;
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            background: #007bff;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .api-links a:hover {
            background: #0056b3;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>{{title}}</h1>
        <p>{{message}}</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        {{#if user}}
        <div class="user-info">
            <h3>Welcome back, {{user.email}}!</h3>
            <p>You are currently logged in.</p>
            {{#if user.role}}
            <p><strong>Role:</strong> {{user.role}}</p>
            {{/if}}
        </div>
        {{else}}
        <p>You are not currently logged in. <a href="/api/login">Login here</a></p>
        {{/if}}
        
        <div class="api-links">
            <h3>Try these API endpoints:</h3>
            <a href="/health">Health Check</a>
            <a href="/api/users/123">Get User</a>
            {{#if user}}
            <a href="/api/profile">Profile</a>
            {{/if}}
        </div>
        
        <h3>Framework Features</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>✅ Type-safe routing with parameter extraction</li>
            <li>✅ Middleware system for request/response processing</li>
            <li>✅ JWT and session-based authentication</li>
            <li>✅ Template engine support (Handlebars, EJS)</li>
            <li>✅ Built-in security middleware (CORS, Helmet, Rate limiting)</li>
            <li>✅ Request validation with schema support</li>
            <li>✅ Error handling with custom error classes</li>
            <li>✅ Static file serving</li>
            <li>✅ Comprehensive logging system</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</body>
</html>